   <abstract xlink:href="http://lib.lsu.edu/services/oralhistory/abstracts/university/distinguished_alumni/Huff_Leona_T730.abs.pdf">Huff discusses her family's life on their farm near Albany, Missouri; her early
            education in Albany; the family's move to Baton Rouge, Louisiana, and their farm on
            Highland Road; the children's attendance at LSU; her study of home economics; student
            life at LSU; and her work for the Emergency Relief Administration during the
            Depression.</abstract>
